      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  (** ** Natural isomorphism respects composition *)\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "#[export] Instance isisomorphism_compose\n         `(T' : @NaturalTransformation C D F' F'')\n         `(T : @NaturalTransformation C D F F')\n         `{@IsIsomorphism (C -> D) F' F'' T'}\n         `{@IsIsomorphism (C -> D) F F' T}\n  : @IsIsomorphism (C -> D) F F'' (T' o T)%natural_transformation\n    := @isisomorphism_compose (C -> D) _ _ T' _ _ T _.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
